They're meditating far from society!
Together, they focus in silence...

A growling stomach pierces the quiet.
Forced to stop, they share a meal!

The pair reaches their spiritual cores...
They both shed their concept of self!

A cat distracts from their focus...
But in their play, they find true bliss!

$aFoes grant 5x SP for the next $a0,
and then 2x SP thereafter! (Only highest
value applied. Does not stack.)
